      "state": "Created",
      "notePath": "rooms/room-why-use-this/notes.txt",
      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-why-use-this/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nThe README frames Knowledge Dungeon as useful for students, developers, researchers, teams, and anyone using mindmaps plus notes.\n\nKey Points\n- Students can use Recall Questions for active memory practice.\n- Developers can map architecture and dependencies as traversable rooms.\n- Teams can build shared onboarding subjects for conventions and workflows.\n\nRecall Question\nWhich user groups are explicitly called out as beneficiaries in the README?",
