      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-ui-home-screen/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nThe home screen manages phase/class selection, subject creation, saved subject browsing, refresh, and admin data tools.\n\nKey Points\n- Users choose phase and study archetype before entering a subject.\n- Saved subjects are listed by name and room count.\n- Desktop adds folder-level import/export helpers in Admin tools.\n\nRecall Question\nWhat core actions does the README assign to the home screen?",
