      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-ui-study-shell/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nThe in-dungeon view keeps study context centralized with HUD, room panel, Phaser canvas, minimap, and map overlay controls.\n\nKey Points\n- HUD exposes progression, navigation, and help controls.\n- Room panel supports topic context, breadcrumbs, portals, and creator edits.\n- The full map can switch between floor-focused and whole-graph views.\n\nRecall Question\nWhich major UI surfaces are described as the main in-dungeon loop workspace?",
