      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-ui-map-navigation/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nThe README highlights floor-aware travel, parent return shortcuts, map panning, and draggable room nodes for navigating deep mindmaps.\n\nKey Points\n- Connected topics are split into same-floor and related-floor travel sections.\n- The map overlay defaults to current-floor filtering with optional whole-graph mode.\n- Users can drag empty canvas to pan and drag nodes to reposition rooms.\n\nRecall Question\nHow does the UI keep deeply nested or multi-floor mindmaps navigable?",
