      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-ui-notes-media/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nScribe-focused note authoring supports lightweight Markdown, preview mode, draft saves, and image attachments with insert helpers.\n\nKey Points\n- Notes support links, emphasis, code, and bullet formatting.\n- Save draft allows iterative writing before all checks pass.\n- Image cards include an Insert in note action to avoid manual markdown token entry.\n\nRecall Question\nWhat note authoring safeguards and media features are called out for Scribe work?",
