      "state": "Created",
      "notePath": "rooms/room-collections-loop/notes.txt",
      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-collections-loop/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nProgression is reinforced with inventory loot, achievement badges, and a diary that reopens collected notes for review.\n\nKey Points\n- Inventory stores artifacts from defeated encounters.\n- Badges reward learning behaviors beyond raw XP totals.\n- Diary entries open full notes as a recall index during review runs.\n\nRecall Question\nHow do Inventory, Badges, and Diary support both motivation and retention?",
