      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-tech-stack/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nKnowledge Dungeon is built with React, Phaser, Zustand, Vite, TypeScript, Electron, Vitest, and ESLint.\n\nKey Points\n- React + Phaser power UI shell and dungeon gameplay rendering.\n- Vite + TypeScript handle build and typing workflows.\n- Electron enables desktop packaging for macOS, Windows, and Linux.\n\nRecall Question\nWhich stack components are named for frontend, desktop, and quality tooling?",
