      "artifactPath": "rooms/room-three-phases/artifact.md",
      "noteText": "Summary\nThe README defines a three-phase learning loop: author topics, clear encounters with notes, then review artifacts and prompts.\n\nKey Points\n- Creator is focused on architecture and graph authoring.\n- Scribe is focused on exploration and rubric-validated note submission.\n- Archaeologist is focused on consolidation and self-check review.\n\nRecall Question\nWhat distinct responsibility does each of the three phases have?",
